# recover the file which is not deleted and also uncommited yet

# recover certain file
$ git checkout <filename>

# recover all files
$ git checkout .

# recover the file to previous No. version
$ git checkout HEAD~NO


# unstaged the file deleted
$ rm file.txt
$ git add file.txt  
Now you want to discard the deleted step of the file 
$ git reset HEAD <filename or .>
$ git chechout <filename or .>
